1956;;My Wife's Family;;British;;Gilbert Gunn;;Ted Ray, Greta Gynt;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/My_Wife%27s_Family_(1956_film);;Jack Gay, a newlywed with a dominating mother-in-law attempts to surprise his wife Stella with a baby grand piano, but when she overhears him discussing it, she mistakes it for an illegitimate child, particularly with the arrival of his ex girlfriend, the blonde and glamorous Gloria Marsh.[4]